# Codebase Structure — Barokah Core POS

Referensi lengkap: `docs/standards/CODEBASE-STRUCTURE.md`

## Monorepo Layout

- `apps/api` — NestJS modular monolith
- `apps/web` — Next.js 15 App Router
- `apps/mobile` — Expo Router
- `packages/shared` — types, constants, utils (no React, no Prisma)
- `packages/ui` — design tokens + React components
- `packages/database` — Prisma only; consumed by API

## Import Rules

```typescript
// ✅ Correct
import { ErrorCodes, formatCurrency } from '@barokah/shared';
import { Button } from '@barokah/ui';
import { apiConfig } from '@/lib/api';

// ❌ Wrong — no cross-app deep imports, no duplicated types
import { x } from '../../../apps/api/src/...';
```

**Never:** `packages/*` importing from `apps/*`.

## NestJS API Structure

```
src/
├── config/
├── common/{filters,interceptors,guards,pipes}/
└── modules/{feature}/
```

- Global `HttpExceptionFilter` + `ResponseInterceptor` in `main.ts`
- Controllers return raw data; interceptor wraps `{ success, data }`
- Business logic in services only

## Where to Put New Code

| Need | Location |
|------|----------|
| Shared type/constant/util | `packages/shared/src/{types,constants,utils}/` |
| Reusable UI component | `packages/ui/src/components/` |
| API feature | `apps/api/src/modules/{feature}/` |
| Web page/component | `apps/web/src/{app,components}/` |
| Mobile screen | `apps/mobile/app/` |

## Scripts Before Handoff

```bash
npm run lint && npm run typecheck && npm run build
```

